{"tid":1693233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"移民及經濟啟示！台股29年新高　新台幣16個月最強","createTime":"2019-11-04T13:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T03:52:34.000Z","uid":29093,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ae42e91e8741e51f61344e1cf623cb928c4f0ec8","tid":1693233,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"移民及經濟啟示！台股29年新高 新台幣16個月最強<br />\n11月04日(一) 18:40<br />\n<br />\n相對港股及港元持續弱勢，台灣則「股匯齊升」，反映外資看好程度。其中，台灣股市周一(4日)突破11,500點大關，收市升157點，報11,556點，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">再創29年以來新高</span></strong>。新台幣亦強勢，新台幣兌每美元報30.405元，創近16個月新高。<br />\n<br />\n據當地證交所統計，外資上周五(1日)總持有股票市值達14.47萬億元新台幣，佔全體上市股票市值的42.08%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1 港元 = 3.8142 新台幣</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"02c96c20a78ad4e03389124b232db85a94fcbc2a","tid":1693233,"uid":29093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"痴線  <br />\n<br />\n29 年新高 <br />\n<br />\n台灣人唔駛投條奶共狗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d85c5e7431d09cf4120150ed56656239aa410d","tid":1693233,"uid":229886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:18:20.000Z","msg":"香港表示: 要不是中共<br />\n香港一早係全亞洲一哥"},{"pid":"0d73cafd1a2c56d48688dbb17505cf9040181723","tid":1693233,"uid":229886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"想問宜家台灣係咪開始睇唔起香港人<br />\n我覺得香港個名愈黎愈臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f1c77261342d8598bf7c0b39721b03f48672e1","tid":1693233,"uid":76735,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"0d73cafd1a2c56d48688dbb17505cf9040181723